It’s been quite a while since we heard any tune from the area fada himself, Charly Boy. But after taking a hiatus from the music scene, he is back with a new track titled “God of Men (Fake Pastors)” and he lends the musical talents of multiple award-winning artiste, Falz. The visuals for “God Of Men (Fake Pastors)” features Nollywood veteran, Segun Arinze while the track was produced by Acesoundz. The video was directed by Unlimited L.A. Watch God Of Men below: 